# 🎙️ Voice-Activated Virtual Assistant

A browser-based virtual assistant built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript that responds to user voice commands using the Web Speech API.

## 🚀 Features

- 🎤 Voice recognition (Speech to Text)
- 🗣️ Speech response (Text to Speech)
- 🕒 Get current time and date
- 🌐 Open websites like YouTube, Facebook, Instagram, WhatsApp
- 💬 Understands greetings and basic commands
- 🔊 Interactive UI with mic animation and effects

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript
- Web Speech API (SpeechRecognition + SpeechSynthesis)

